had rendered outstand ing service as a teacher and prin cipal of the Stanton High School in Jacksonville He lamented the fact that in the teaching of his tory in our schools the story of the Negro is omitted He decided to do something about it He wrote books dramatizing the strivings of the Negro upward His Black Manhattan is an im portant chapter in the history of the Negro in the United States Speaking more expliciy about"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-03-01T09:35:34.811Z", "group": ["ndnp/curiv", "university-of-california-riverside-riverside-ca-awardee"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/resource/sn82016196/1949-01-06/ed-1/?sp=3", "image_url": ["https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:curiv:batch_curiv_archylee_ver01:data:sn82016196:00516992438:1949010601:0003/full/pct:6.25/0/default.jpg#h=483&w=349", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:curiv:batch_curiv_archylee_ver01:data:sn82016196:00516992438:1949010601:0003/full/pct:12.5/0/default.jpg#h=967&w=699", "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service?segment=/service/ndnp/curiv/batch_curiv_archylee_ver01/data/sn82016196/00516992438/1949010601/0003.xml&format=alto_xml"], "index": 3, "language": ["english"], "location": ["los angeles county", "california", "los angeles", "united states"], "location_city": ["los angeles"], "location_country": ["united states"], "location_county": ["los angeles"], "location_state": ["california"], "mime_type": ["image/jp2", "application/pdf", "text/xml", "image/jpeg", "image/jpeg", "application/json", "text/plain"], "number": ["9", "5", "0", "8", "3", "sn82016196", "4", "0000000003", "6", "2", "1"], "number_edition": ["1"], "number_lccn": ["sn82016196"], "number_page": ["0000000003"], "number_reel": ["0", "0", "5", "1", "6", "9", "9", "2", "4", "3", "8"], "online_format": ["image", "pdf", "online text"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "other_title": ["Eagle"], "partof": ["serial and government publicati